     <h1>Waiver Wire Pickup Guide</h1>
     

     <p>Mastering the waiver wire is a crucial part of having a winning team in fantasy basketball. Below you can learn the main things to consider when deciding who to pickup.  <p>
     </p>
     <h3>1. Last 7 and PR7</h3>
     <p>
      When deciding who to pick up off the waivers, start off looking at the players stats. Stats that you should play particulary close attention to is fantasy points per game then sort by "Last 7". This will give you a great idea on how the player is doing most recently. Then click the "Research" tab on the player list and sort by "PR7" (Player Rating Last 7) to see if anyone else stands out.</span> 
 </p>
